data.description: Location, Location. Property is located in a desirable area in North San Gabriel.  Close to award winning elementary school.  This single story features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, spacious living room with fireplace, large window for lots of sunlight, dining area with family room and a fenced pool which is great for entertainment for family and guests. The kitchen has cherry wood cabinets, granite countertops with eating area & bar counter for extra seating.  The property has a long driveway for extra parking or RV parking, large front yard and backyard with fruit trees. The roof is only 5 years old and the central air unit was upgraded two years ago. This can be your dream home with some TLC. This property will not last.
